msgid ""
"Learning how to stay safe really helped us. The other day, my daughter got invited to a party by an older boy, and he said he would pay for her transport. Before, she would just go secretly, but now she came to me to talk about it.\n"
"\n"
"We reminded each other that it is important to see the warning signs and stay safe, and she decided to say ‚Äòno‚Äô. I am so proud of her. Even me, I now know that others should not pressure or convince me to do something. I can give the right example to my children."
msgstr ""
"Kujifunza namna ya kuwa salama hakika  imetusaidia  sisi. Siku moja binti yangu alipewa mualiko kwenye sherehe na mvulana mkubwa, na alisema atamlipia usafiri. Kabla, alikua akienda kwa siri, lakini kwa sasa alikuja kwangu akaniambia kuhusu hilo.\n"
"\n"
"Tulikumbushana kila mmoja wetu kwamba ni muhimu kuona ishara za onyo na kukaa salama, na aliamua kusema ' hapana ' ninajivunia sana yeye. Hata mimi, Sasa ninafahamu kwamba wengine hawawezi kunishinikiza au kunishawishi kufanya kitu chochote. Ninaweza kutoa mfano sahihi kwa watoto wangu."

#. type=data_list
